{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/kalau-kamu-pecinta-kucing-kamu-harus-baca-artikel-ini/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Kalau kamu Pecinta Kucing, Kamu Harus Baca Artikel Ini","content":"<p>Kalau kamu suka dengan kucing, pasti bakal suka juga deh sama <em>game mobile</em> Neko Atsume. Sudah pernah dengar? Sebelumnya, memang ada banyak banget <em>game</em> yang mengajak pemainnya untuk merawat binatang peliharaan secara virtual lewat aplikasi <em>smartphone</em>. Nah, Neko Atsume adalah<em> mobile app game</em> yang di-<em>publish</em> pertama kali di 2014 dan telah berhasil mengambil hati para pecinta kucing. Terutama bagi orang-orang yang ingin pelihara binatang imut ini tapi gak sempat karena sibuk dengan kegiatannya. Kucing bisa dirawat dalam aplikasi Neko Atsume. Kucingnya juga bisa diberi nama dan personality-personality yang unik, jadi pemain dari game harus pintar-pintar memberikan <em>treat </em>secara berbeda ke setiap kucing yang ada di halaman rumah.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8943\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8943\" data-attachment-id=\"8943\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kalau-kamu-pecinta-kucing-kamu-harus-baca-artikel-ini/attachment/1-65/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-19.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Neko Atsume (Sumber: tumblr.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Neko Atsume (Sumber: tumblr.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-19.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-19.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8943\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-19.jpg\" alt=\"Neko Atsume (Sumber: tumblr.com)Neko Atsume (Sumber: tumblr.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8943\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Neko Atsume (Sumber: tumblr.com)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8959\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8959\" data-attachment-id=\"8959\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kalau-kamu-pecinta-kucing-kamu-harus-baca-artikel-ini/attachment/4-59/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-18.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Neko Atsume (Sumber: etsy.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Neko Atsume (Sumber: etsy.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-18.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-18.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8959\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-18.jpg\" alt=\"Neko Atsume (Sumber: etsy.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8959\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Neko Atsume (Sumber: etsy.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Berkat kesuksesan dari <em>game mobile</em>-nya, Neko Atsume  membuat film <em>live action-</em>nya pada April 2017 lalu. Di live action Neko Atsume menceritakan kehisupan penulis novel, Masaru yang sering mendapat <em>writer’s block. </em>Suatu hari ia pindah ke pinggir kota dan tinggal di rumah baru untuk mencari inspirasi. Di rumah itu Ia bertemu dengan seekor kucing di halaman rumah. Semenjak Ia merawat kucing-kucing yang datang ke rumah, rasa cemas dalam dirinya pun perlahan hilang dan mengubahnya menjadi orang yang lebih ceria. Masaru juga bisa menulis cerita yang menarik dan diakui oleh atasan di kantor. Film ini juga terdapat selipan <em>romance</em> yang membuat alur cerita gak membosankan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8947\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8947\" data-attachment-id=\"8947\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kalau-kamu-pecinta-kucing-kamu-harus-baca-artikel-ini/attachment/6-34/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Live Action Neko Atsume (Sumber: pinterest)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Live Action Neko Atsume (Sumber: pinterest)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-8.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8947\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-8.jpg\" alt=\"Live Action Neko Atsume (Sumber: pinterest)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8947\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Live Action Neko Atsume (Sumber: pinterest)</p></div></p>\n<p>Seperti yang kita tau, orang Jepang suka banget dengan kucing. Bahkan mereka percaya dan bergantung dengan kucing sejak jaman dulu. Kucing yang dipelihara oleh masyarakat Jepang dulu sering membantu para petani dengan membasmi tikus sawah, jadi panen pun bisa sukses. Ada juga patung Maneki-neko yang dipercayai membawa rezeki dan wajib dimiliki oleh orang yang membuka usaha agar dagangannya laris.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8955\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8955\" data-attachment-id=\"8955\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kalau-kamu-pecinta-kucing-kamu-harus-baca-artikel-ini/attachment/3-65/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-19.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: cba.ca)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: cba.ca)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-19.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-19.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8955\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-19.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: cba.ca)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8955\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: cba.ca)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8945\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8945\" data-attachment-id=\"8945\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kalau-kamu-pecinta-kucing-kamu-harus-baca-artikel-ini/attachment/5-48/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: catster.jpg)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: catster.jpg)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8945\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-12.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: catster.jpg)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8945\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: catster.jpg)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kucing keturunan ras Jepang yang murni adalah <em>Japanese Bobtail, </em>yang sesuai dengan namanya yaitu memiliki ekor pendek. Menurut legendanya dulu ada kucing yang ekornya gak sengaja menyentuh api. Api yang ada dari ekor si kucing akhirnya membuat banyak rumah ikut terbakar, jadi Kaisar menyuruh agar setiap kucing yang ada di jalan harus dipotong ekornya. Tapi itu cuma legenda aja kok! Aslinya, ekor pendek dari <em>Japanese Bobtail</em> adalah hasil dari mutasi percampuran gen.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8957\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8957\" data-attachment-id=\"8957\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kalau-kamu-pecinta-kucing-kamu-harus-baca-artikel-ini/attachment/2-52/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-13.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Japanese Bobtail (Sumber: wikipedia)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Japanese Bobtail (Sumber: wikipedia)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-13.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-13.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8957\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-13.jpg\" alt=\"Japanese Bobtail (Sumber: wikipedia)Japanese Bobtail (Sumber: wikipedia)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8957\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Japanese Bobtail (Sumber: wikipedia)</p></div></p>\n<p>Memelihara kucing adalah tren dan uda jadi hal yang umum banget di Jepang. Bagi orang yang gak bisa memelihara di rumah, banyak kafe kucing yang tersebar diseluruh negeri Jepang. Hewan satu ini memang imut banget dan cuma dengan melihat tingkahnya aja bisa melepas stress seseorang. Kalau kamu sudah menonton film Neko Atsume no Ie, mainin <em>game</em>-nya di <em>smartphone</em> kamu, atau bahkan cuma suka aja dengan kucing, coba lihat <em>photo book</em> dari filmnya juga deh! Perusahaan pembuat aplikasi Neko Atsume juga sudah merilis <em>official book</em> berisi info tentang kucing-kucing yang ada dalam game loh. Duh… lucu-lucu banget dan bikin gemes!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"6e569b43-5873-504d-893a-1d195c17aad4"}}}